127095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:09:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686472ffd35a613dc0e4bec5fe0cd648ff1ef723","tid":437251,"uid":87257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油啊你地 我都覺得 即使同學每個party都會邀請你 然後我又有去 但去到都唔知做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eced8f11491e6003dce20276960fc1a6715c826","tid":437251,"uid":130440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:31:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油啊你地 我都覺得 即使同學每個party都會邀請你 然後我又有去 但去到都唔知做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我平時都冇乜野 <br />\n係一多野做就好想逃避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你嘅勉勵說話 起碼我可以上黎噏下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好期待返香港呀 哈哈<br />\n我自己唔算係主動嗰啲人 好多時候都係做好自己就夠<br />\n第一年都冇乜聊同學講野<br />\n會唔會係因為我少講野而令人怕左我呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時父母問啲同學點我都唔知點答佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好彩而家開學返學校都同到啲一齊做野嘅同學傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜我交心嘅朋友全部都係香港 唉"},{"pid":"9327302ffecb2a916eeb2290fe4df00727960be3","tid":437251,"uid":127095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4196c06e7a74f0a24a717b6a7e8acb170c44d2","tid":437251,"uid":83718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油啊你地 我都覺得 即使同學每個party都會邀請你 然後我又有去 但去到都唔知做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我平時都冇乜野 <br />\n係一多野做就好想逃避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你嘅勉勵說話 起碼我可以上黎噏下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好期待返香港呀 哈哈<br />\n我自己唔算係主動嗰啲人 好多時候都係做好自己就夠<br />\n第一年都冇乜聊同學講野<br />\n會唔會係因為我少講野而令人怕左我呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時父母問啲同學點我都唔知點答佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好彩而家開學返學校都同到啲一齊做野嘅同學傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜我交心嘅朋友全部都係香港 唉</blockquote><br />\n我明你個種倒數返香港既感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實去到外國 大家都係湊合 又點會多真心朋友<br />\n你中意既隨時都可以上黎廢up嫁喎<br />\n我都係交心朋友係哂香港 而家係外國都係做project食飯玩下先一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時間我會自己逛下<br />\nI know your feelings<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e78e7789608b833774a1684ef6df3564957bad","tid":437251,"uid":83718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中意你個句 在好遠既地方 有人同你身同感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱呀 但你真係要正面啲 英文麻麻就聽多啲睇多啲用多啲英文溝通 唔好諗自殺啦<br />\n我已經聽講好多人過外國有抑鬱呀自殺傾向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10230a638f1e355be4b16ae4b9663f30254ed67","tid":437251,"uid":83718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油啊你地 我都覺得 即使同學每個party都會邀請你 然後我又有去 但去到都唔知做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你都加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有時候都唔明 唔啱傾去黎做乜"},{"pid":"1d9a7cb8861858f8ed5207b603f40f9bb1870af9","tid":437251,"uid":83718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGood idea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔太識用tg"},{"pid":"0c36279c6fccc15fc63f0a9e0e49fdcb11853f80","tid":437251,"uid":106156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:37:37.000Z","msg":"有冇英國撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb902661a8780b57db7f5f3721e252035a395f35","tid":437251,"uid":83718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:45:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇英國撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係 但聖誕準備去聖誕玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40841636aed9a2c3f635b312953f1bc86e246d7","tid":437251,"uid":83718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:50:06.000Z","msg":"大家 我準備開個tg group俾大家吹下水<br />\n你地知啦去外國咁撚寂寞係需要勉勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/st_haha\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fst_haha&d=0JFroFfiJkW7YaJglK%2BOKP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9dbd1225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/st_haha</a><br />\n<br />\n加我啦然後加你地入group傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2badbb35081a127fa25b70e6ad708fb513e132a6","tid":437251,"uid":83718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇英國撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係 但聖誕準備去聖誕玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌手殘 係聖誕準備去<span style=\"color: red;\">英國</span>玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53c8108e6830ab6c7ca0b5817fdf41ce2d50877","tid":437251,"uid":147445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:55:56.000Z","msg":"我反而好享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好鍾意不停單機<br />\n<br />\n自己又可能煮下野，四處獨遊<br />\n<br />\n完全唔想返HK<br />\n<br />\n上一年一話唔返去，即刻比老母屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果都係返去2星期即走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319b859cd2105d524246153a33051aaf728ec4a4","tid":437251,"uid":83718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T23:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而好享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好鍾意不停單機<br />\n<br />\n自己又可能煮下野，四處獨遊<br />\n<br />\n完全唔想返HK<br />\n<br />\n上一年一話唔返去，即刻比老母屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果都係返去2星期即走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你中意單機咁唔怪得知你享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我都係掛住屋企 想旅行 又想家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571f6d8e3c6c56dba3b2a3892ec6a3f9f78932fc","tid":437251,"uid":83718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T23:02:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家留tg啦快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"3c03c5bd497595219e08f8481f8a472c0c63ce97","tid":437251,"uid":71189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T23:08:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇英國撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英國jj<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50dca4d46560107d1a0ef8ec2499f248ee2e70c","tid":437251,"uid":147445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T23:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我反而好享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好鍾意不停單機<br />\n<br />\n自己又可能煮下野，四處獨遊<br />\n<br />\n完全唔想返HK<br />\n<br />\n上一年一話唔返去，即刻比老母屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果都係返去2星期即走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你中意單機咁唔怪得知你享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我都係掛住屋企 想旅行 又想家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁咪同屋企一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nor叫佢地飛過黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12f0e0b84b0aaa8cb407c1c0d6abb7fbc674740","tid":437251,"uid":142754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T23:14:17.000Z","msg":"身邊好多香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都係好摺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfec2519713fd390982572f4d9591a10b0316db","tid":437251,"uid":127176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T23:16:28.000Z","msg":"我唔擅於結交朋友<br />\n不過有幸係度識到幾個香港人朋友，就咁組成咗個固定圈子<br />\n至於外國朋友唔係冇，不過都係一個一個咁識，入唔到人地嘅圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢地都唔係好多話題傾，都係同番香港人先吹得埋<br />\n其實我個人好簡單，只要佢地真心當我朋友已經足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：英國jj"},{"pid":"982ad5a75e7076919764c7a3a12f512770947910","tid":437251,"uid":62162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T23:18:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/hkukstudentnet/about/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fhkukstudentnet%2Fabout%2F&d=0JFroFfiJkW7YaJglK%2BOKP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=0a7fd523\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/hkukstudentnet/about/</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣加入本telegram group請pm本page inbox"},{"pid":"7b8fd6c2e725493c5d253bdfbdc79ff61ccb8166","tid":437251,"uid":127176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T23:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似係⋯聽到人地講英文就覺得多一層隔閡⋯唯有講廣東話既先可以暢所欲言咁交心<br />\n利申：最愛廣東話</blockquote><br />\n我都想講下英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家每日講普通話仲多過英文同廣東話<br />\n想瘋狂講廣東話呀嗚嗚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔係自己語言又唔係當地語言<br />\n有時我明知人地係大陸人都會照同佢講英文"},{"pid":"b7ce23ddcc8ab8eb3b607f14fab16dcdb634efe9","tid":437251,"uid":83718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T23:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我反而好享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好鍾意不停單機<br />\n<br />\n自己又可能煮下野，四處獨遊<br />\n<br />\n完全唔想返HK<br />\n<br />\n上一年一話唔返去，即刻比老母屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果都係返去2星期即走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你中意單機咁唔怪得知你享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我都係掛住屋企 想旅行 又想家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁咪同屋企一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nor叫佢地飛過黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好難嫁話哂都咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我寧願時間快啲過我快啲返去"},{"pid":"9a98466ab260e31255c3dd89e5f7542bb0f2ae8a","tid":437251,"uid":83718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T23:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身邊好多香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都係好摺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我間學校勁多香港人<br />\n但人地一堆堆我識唔到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9f389b3d422e9fc0d6f864a907af75ec7a7d04","tid":437251,"uid":83718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T23:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔擅於結交朋友<br />\n不過有幸係度識到幾個香港人朋友，就咁組成咗個固定圈子<br />\n至於外國朋友唔係冇，不過都係一個一個咁識，入唔到人地嘅圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢地都唔係好多話題傾，都係同番香港人先吹得埋<br />\n其實我個人好簡單，只要佢地真心當我朋友已經足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：英國jj</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗 最慘係冇乜真心同啱傾朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想識返幾個香港朋友組圈子<br />\n起碼傾計幾好 又去下玩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}